$BITALIC A. $EITALIC  \(\displaystyle\lim_{x\to a^+} f(x) \not = f(a) \)
$BR$BR
$BITALIC B. $EITALIC The \(\displaystyle\lim_{x\to a^+} f(x)\) doesn't exist.
$BR$BR
$BITALIC C. $EITALIC The function is not defined at the point given.
$BR$BR
